      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions span the full clinical CPB range. Analog fluid properties are within established equivalence bounds for hemolysis surrogate testing. Validation activities are directly representative of COU conditions. Gradation 2 satisfied."
