    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility for the intended COU at MRL 2. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required gradation levels. Six factors were appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. The model demonstrates adequate discretization control (GCI < 2%), validated output agreement within 8% of experimental benchmark data, and satisfies the RH < 1 clinical acceptance criterion at all five operating conditions. The package is accepted for regulatory submission support.",
